        <path fillRule='evenodd' clipRule='evenodd'
              d='M21.875 12.875H15.125V6.125C15.125 5.50288 14.621 5 14 5C13.379 5 12.875 5.50288 12.875 6.125V12.875H6.125C5.504 12.875 5 13.3779 5 14C5 14.6221 5.504 15.125 6.125 15.125H12.875V21.875C12.875 22.4971 13.379 23 14 23C14.621 23 15.125 22.4971 15.125 21.875V15.125H21.875C22.496 15.125 23 14.6221 23 14C23 13.3779 22.496 12.875 21.875 12.875Z'
              fill='currentColor'/>
        <mask id='mask0' mask-type='alpha' maskUnits='userSpaceOnUse' x='5' y='5' width='18' height='18'>
            <path fillRule='evenodd' clipRule='evenodd'
                  d='M21.875 12.875H15.125V6.125C15.125 5.50288 14.621 5 14 5C13.379 5 12.875 5.50288 12.875 6.125V12.875H6.125C5.504 12.875 5 13.3779 5 14C5 14.6221 5.504 15.125 6.125 15.125H12.875V21.875C12.875 22.4971 13.379 23 14 23C14.621 23 15.125 22.4971 15.125 21.875V15.125H21.875C22.496 15.125 23 14.6221 23 14C23 13.3779 22.496 12.875 21.875 12.875Z'
                  fill='currentColor'/>
        </mask>
        <g mask='url(#mask0)'>
        </g>
    </svg>
)

            <mask id='mask0' mask-type='alpha' maskUnits='userSpaceOnUse' x='4' y='11' width='16' height='2'>
